Hi guys,

I´m searching this part "Size3.Size2.Tank". On KerbalX I can find it and its telling me that this is a part from a mod "squadexpansion". But this mod dont appear anywhere and I cant remember that i have installed this mod.
I had installed many mods, so i cant tell anymore but i thought i build a fully stock craft without modparts.
Please help me finding this part, i cant load my craft anymore.

Thank you for your help.

Edited June 28, 2018 by Gryphus_1
Isn’t this related to the Making History expansion pack?

My google fu is showing that @Cavscout74 might have some insight into this.  But the page it's linking too is not much help, as it's a list of all his recent posts, and I'm not digging through all that.
I'm pretty sure that's from the Making History DLC.

If it's the same part, it was somehow tied into the Missing History mod, which requires the Making History DLC.  Missing History resized & retextured some Making History parts if you have the DLC, plus added a few parts like size adapters.  I'm not exactly sure of details, because that part disappeared in my 1.4.3 install when I updated to the (then) newest version of Missing History mod, but it was in an older version.  My 1.4 install is messed up right now, so until you might be have better luck on the mod's topic.
